th\nmethods that avoid platinum impurities for an investigation of intrinsic\nphysical properties of iridates, and possible superconducting phases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 16:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-18"}
