ators with masses below 1 keV for\ncoupling products $\\sqrt{g_\\nu g_e}$ $\\sim$ $1 \\times 10^{-6}~(9.5 \\times\n10^{-7})$ and $1\\times 10^{-7} ~(8\\times 10^{-8})$, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 17:37:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 06:05:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-12"}
