ackground rejection in the ROI, but moreover, the\nincrease in detection efficiency, push the ANAIS-112 sensitivity to test the\nDAMA/LIBRA annual modulation result beyond 3$\\sigma$ with three-year exposure,\nbeing possible to reach 5$\\sigma$ by extending the data taking for a few more\nyears than the scheduled 5 years which were due in August 2022.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2022 14:02:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 09:42:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
