tively. Our findings will be beneficial in the\ndevelopment of ultra-thin graphene-based multistate photonic devices for\ndigital switching, sensing in terahertz regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2022 15:37:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
